<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Concerned Citizens in Cancer Alley Vow to Ramp Up Battle Against Industrial Pollution in 2018</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row">
<div class="columns small-12 medium-4 sidebar-left">
<div class="entry-meta">
